query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from tag_question AS tq
inner join question AS q
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.favorite_count >= 0 AND q.favorite_count <= 1
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('2d',
'automated-tests',
'bit-manipulation',
'get',
'integration-testing',
'linq-to-entities',
'namespaces',
'popup',
'ssl-certificate',
'timeout',
'webforms',
'webrtc',
'windows-services',
'wix',
'xcode6');
